Description: Rename JPG files using Dolphin/Konqueror
 kde-service-menu-reimage is a package that extends the functionalities of Dolphin
 or Konqueror adding many additionally sensible menu, reachables with right
 click on the files. It's similar to gnome nautilus actions.
 These actions are related to pdf files.
 .
 You can rename jpg and tiff files with data content in Exif metadata.
 For example: 001.jpg -> 2018-04-27_133741.jpg
